    "updated_at": "2016-06-13T10:39:58Z",
    "body": "@mk213 The `webFrame.setSpellCheckProvider` only deals with iterating words and reporting wrong words, it doesn't know which language the word belongs to. The spell checker under `ru-RU` probably just discards all non-russian words, while when language is German it is hard to distinguish English words. \n"
